  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Recommended update for mailx",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "\nThis update for mailx enables IPv6 support and includes the following \nfixes:\n\n    * Crop off the brackets of an ipv6 address if found. (bnc#853246)\n    * Enable mailx to parse IPv6 addresses including a port ([ipv6]:port).\n      (bnc#853246)\n    * Do not pseudo detect Latin nor UTF-8 in binary attachments.\n      (bnc#827010)\n\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
